You are working on Momentum Fitness, a premium gym and fitness website UI built with Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, ShadCN UI, and Google Stitch designs.

IMPORTANT:

- This project currently uses ONLY frontend
- UI designs are created using Google Stitch
- Maintain Stitch-generated design consistency
- Do NOT redesign existing layouts unnecessarily
- Follow the same spacing, typography, colors, and component patterns from Stitch
- Extend existing design system carefully

## Current Project Scope

Frontend only project.

## Tech Stack

- Next.js App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- ShadCN UI
- Lucide React
- Framer Motion

## Design System Rules

The project uses Google Stitch generated UI.

When generating code:

- Match existing Stitch layout structure
- Keep same design language
- Reuse existing section styles
- Reuse existing card styles
- Reuse existing spacing system
- Reuse typography scale
- Reuse button variants
- Reuse existing shadows and border radius
- Avoid inconsistent UI patterns

## UI Style

Momentum Fitness should feel:

- Modern
- Premium
- Athletic
- Energetic
- Minimal
- Professional

## Pages

- Home
- About
- Pricing
- Trainers
- Contact
- Gallery
- FAQ
- Terms
- Privacy

